Sharon Angela https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sharon_Angela 0 Sharon Angela is an American film and television actress, screenwriter, and film director. Angela is known for her portrayal of Rosalie Aprile on the HBO series The Sopranos. Sharon_Angela is an_American_film_and_television_actress , screenwriter , and film_director .
